@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_wsmgxk(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.exp(v0)
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.exp(wp.cos(tmp + 0.35)))
    tmp = wp.abs(0.92)
    tmp = (wp.abs(wp.sin(v2 + 1.00)) * v1)
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.sin((tmp + 0.85 - v2 + 0.23)))
    v2 = (0.99 * ((tmp + 0.71 / tmp + 0.12) / (tmp + 0.97 * v0 + 0.23)))
    data[tid] = v0
